## Changelog
### Features
* 7ee10715b4e2df9fe2cefee124f1eedb6fc10179 feat: Make re-add add and remove entries in exact_ directories
### Fixes
* aa188e608963a5e66c384d1713ac18517a029ba4 fix: Make all template funcs available in diff and merge args
* 72c7d0b134d30b8748d5e18ea74feb7b5f784a8e fix: Ignore special-use domains when extracting hostname from /etc/hosts
* 35b22c8243a059f7ad11d5f107fe4b8e1d58f6e4 fix: Fix fromIni | toIni template func round trip with quoted strings
* d3a403496b6d92f70f48b8a251bcc11fa3c4d0d0 fix: Fix pattern in install script
### Documentation
* 8591960c5b55b27d3806c6754232e1a6980957e1 docs: Add link to article
* 3aff7ac8765ae3913dc39e387ae8883e2f542ca3 docs: Improve description of --create flag
* 95516545b97767bd1e9d1d3071275faaf839b850 docs: Update VSCode merge tool instructions to handles spaces in paths
* 16946dd5b2357e956dd86aa7e67a68107829e4f1 docs: Add main-branch/chezroot to list of related software
* ee2f0a2118c13ee0690de3b846b2a0eaedca2db4 docs: Fix generate command example
### Other
* 4785bf3a97ca02fd9eada92f5eb5edc878438294 Update documentation for --create option in add.md
